        "description": "# “Let’s start a Journey! To our tomorrow!”\n\nAs a member of the renowned RUINSMAGUS Guild, your goal is to help strengthen it with magic, resources – and wisdom! – as you embark on more than 25 unique, story-driven quests. \n{351937041257287}\n\n\nFace off against guardians tasked with protecting the ruins from intruders – and solve the deadly puzzles hidden within. When you've succeeded, head to the surface to acquire new items and upgrade your equipment in town – if you want to live another day, that is!\n{1298633201098030}\n\n# Features\n- Immersive VR mechanics bring the world to life.\n\n- More than 25 story-driven quests to challenge your skills.\n\n- Unleash 16 unique spells from the palm of your hand.\n\n- Raise your shield with to block enemy attacks.\n\n- Cast and blink your way through a stunning VR fantasy world.\n\n- Equip new armor, gauntlets, and shields to stack the odds in your favor!\n{3782892395315941}",
